Name: A Faroese spellchecking dictionary
URL: http://www.stava.fo/
Version: 1.0
Update Mechanism: Manual (https://crbug.com/422924606)
License File: LICENSE_en_US.txt
Security Critical: no
Shipped: yes
Description:
This folder contains a partial copy of the Faroese dictionary for hunspell. It consists of a dictionary file, an affix file, and a license file. (It does not include installation scripts used by Firefox.)
